Manchester United beat Manchester City 4-1 in the Premier League at Old Trafford . 
  Sergio Aguero opened the scoring for City in the 14th minute . 
  Ashley Young and Marouane Fellaini doubled the Red Devils lead in the 28th . 
  Juan Mata and Chris Smalling completed the scoring in the 73rd minute . 
  Aguero scored a late consolation for Manuel Pellegrini's side . 
 